{"tid":800984,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家對留住Ex既野有咩睇法","createTime":"2018-08-31T09:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T19:20:25.000Z","uid":205492,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3fed381054945e8d3052ac9e48e4b1b9c4e876c7","tid":800984,"uid":205492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:26:54.000Z","msg":"事情是咁的<br />\n話說小弟有一日十萬個唔好彩見返ex<br />\n分手之前 佢就有個袋漏左係我到 <br />\n咁我就覺得袋呢啲常用品扔左佢好似好哂<br />\n而且係完好無缺<br />\n所以無扔到留住左攞去用喇 <br />\n<br />\n見返佢個日咁岩就比佢見到我用個袋<br />\n之後就係到同人叫哂春咁講<br />\n唔係分左手好耐喇咩<br />\n你留住個袋托柒呢啲說話喇<br />\n即係扮哂上菜咁既款喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到咁講之後我真係完全無言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家點睇係咪分手真係有必要扔哂所有野<br />\n姐係有用既野都要扔左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：分左手好耐 無感情可言"},{"pid":"bff2d05eacacfdfffb69f62e6bd50f41e1fd8b62","tid":800984,"uid":138728,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:30:57.000Z","msg":"個心唔係到 望到佢啲野都唔會有感覺 <br />\n除非執野見到好阻掟 唔係都唔會特登扔"},{"pid":"aedda1f0da7e2b213cb98f544a1685ac36983111","tid":800984,"uid":7814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"男人老狗用女人袋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"04478a560cee2b7b355611924a4fdfb92c8b2a26","tid":800984,"uid":205492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aedda1f0da7e2b213cb98f544a1685ac36983111","tid":800984,"uid":7814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"男人老狗用女人袋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"男女通用架ching"},{"pid":"3fc8c9b5366ab0aa8b6e8206754c3be4bb44acc4","tid":800984,"uid":137540,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:34:48.000Z","msg":"純粹因為樣野仲有用 用得冇乜必要當垃圾唔要<br />\n對ex已經冇感覺 望住樣野都唔會諗起乜嘢"},{"pid":"508ef71f273a809aa026f538dad61ef69266e0aa","tid":800984,"uid":86948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:36:28.000Z","msg":"臭"},{"pid":"f1a218cc70bb9ddd963df361b50499b841d63ec0","tid":800984,"uid":150053,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:36:42.000Z","msg":"純粹唔好浪費<br />\n照用,激柒死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf4dda4d1d35aabc2dec20c693ccb294a511ed7","tid":800984,"uid":205492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1a218cc70bb9ddd963df361b50499b841d63ec0","tid":800984,"uid":150053,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:36:42.000Z","msg":"純粹唔好浪費<br />\n照用,激柒死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了 唔想再咁唔好彩見到佢"},{"pid":"70e87f61c09a58e38b868fb418d0ff5ceff7716a","tid":800984,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:07:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dd6a0eee8011e61bbe716ca2e562085f13e97e1","tid":800984,"uid":205492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70e87f61c09a58e38b868fb418d0ff5ceff7716a","tid":800984,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:07:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:10:54.000Z","msg":"有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388ecf8c4585c3f52d5511b50a71b83ebbaa9932","tid":800984,"uid":172844,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"基本上分咗手都冇特別丟野<br />\n送果d野都擺晒係屋企<br />\n個人唔啱姐<br />\n件物件冇做錯野喎"},{"pid":"3af1a4d8ee18ebcef29550ce143977c1667bbede","tid":800984,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":